{"main_content":"<div id=\"tabSelect\"> <h1>Module 3: Testing<\/h1> <a href=\"\/3\/1\" class=\"nextTab\" style=\"display: inline-block;\">Intro <\/a> <a href=\"\/3\/2\" class=\"nextTab\" style=\"display: inline-block;\">Videos<\/a> <a href=\"\/3\/3\" class=\"currentTab\" style=\"display: inline-block;\">Quiz<\/a> <\/div> <form id=\"assessmentPage\" method=\"POST\" action=\"results\" onselectstart=\"return false;\"> <h2>Quiz<\/h2> <p class=\"visionQuiz\">  <label for=\"vision1\">1. An applicant may have a medical condition affecting their vision or  a disease of the eyes if:<\/label>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision1\" value=\"1\">A. They complain of blurry vision<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision1\" value=\"2\">B. They say they are unable to see the center of a road sign<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision1\" value=\"3\">C. They say they are unable to see the outer edge of a road sign<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision1\" value=\"4\">D. All of the above<\/span> <\/p> <p class=\"visionQuiz\">  <label for=\"vision2\">2. An applicant\u2019s vision \u2014 specifically their ability to recognize or interpret  road signs \u2014 can be affected by a disease of the eyes or a disease of the  brain (like dementia, stroke, etc.):<\/label>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision2\" value=\"1\">True<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision2\" value=\"2\">False<\/span> <\/p> <p class=\"visionQuiz\">  <label for=\"vision3\">3. If an applicant has a medical condition affecting their head and neck  movement:<\/label>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision3\" value=\"1\">A. They may have difficulty placing their head in the vision machine<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision3\" value=\"2\">B. They may have difficulty scanning their environment while driving<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision3\" value=\"3\">C. They are probably just getting old and experiencing age-related changes that do not impact driving safety<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision3\" value=\"4\">D. Both A and B<\/span> <\/p> <p class=\"visionQuiz\">  <label for=\"vision4\">4. If an applicant hesitates for a long time or appears confused with  directions during the test, it could be a sign of a medical condition  affecting vision or memory and thinking skills:<\/label>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision4\" value=\"1\">True<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision4\" value=\"2\">False<\/span> <\/p> <p class=\"visionQuiz\">  <label for=\"vision5\">5. Good vision and understanding road signs is essential for safe driving.  It is the standard the state has set to qualify an applicant for driving.  An applicant\u2019s ability to complete the test independently is important:<\/label>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision5\" value=\"1\">True<\/span>  <span>  <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vision5\" value=\"2\">False<\/span> <\/p> <p>  <button type=\"submit\">Quiz results<\/button> <\/p> <\/form>","page_title":"Module 3: Quiz"}